.SH EXAMPLES
.PP
.I Run openswitcher in a terminal:
.TP
1. Select the text
.TP
2. \fBxkb-switch -n && xsel | sudo openswitcher --emulate\fR

.PP
.I Run openswitcher in a grafical environment:
.TP
1. Select the text
.TP
2. Press default \fBCtr_L+Alt_L\fR shortcut

